      "content": "makes sense, the vibes are definitely heavy. to really ground this in a specific urban setting for the script, i want to get more specific with the visual identity of the neighborhood. could you add some details about the demographics of these groups? like, what racial or ethnic backgrounds would typically be associated with this kind of environment to make the setting feel more authentic and realistic for a gritty crime drama?",
